-- a needle that is absent everywhere prunes all granules
Granules: 6/6
Granules: 0/6
-- the index is recognized by force_data_skipping_indices
3
-- a single-word needle has no complete token, so it cannot prune, but results stay correct
1	Well, Hello ClickHouse !
2	Well, Hello World !
4	Say Hello !
1	Well, Hello ClickHouse !
2	Well, Hello World !
4	Say Hello !
Granules: 6/6
-- an empty needle array is always false
0
